{"tid":2023763,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"何謂「偶像」","createTime":"2020-05-19T08:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T10:38:34.000Z","uid":231600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"587cd80984765541e9f260de08ff6255c273cf02","tid":2023763,"uid":231600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:02:32.000Z","msg":"所謂「偶像」，就是一樣令人「愛上」的職業。<br />\n<br />\n任何人都可以是偶像，不論男女老少。一旦踏入這個「領域」。你就要負上責任去令人們開心，高興。<br />\n<br />\n不能再以玩樂的心態成為「偶像」。<br />\n<br />\n有的人認為「偶像」只是一種虛名，所以就以不上不下的態度面對這個神聖職業，利用半桶水的性格去吸引眾人的目光。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">舉個例子，現今的YOUTUBER，口口聲聲話自己係宅男偶像，但只會賣弄肉體。</span></span><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">她們根本不知道觀眾需要的是什麼。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他們看似降低了難度，實際上半調子的心態只會令目標更加困難，只會跟風的人根本當不成偶像。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她們只是「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雞，妓女，她們什麼都不是！</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由現在起，我，才是真正的偶像。"},{"pid":"b4e766541c1eb97ad7c47941354d6cac98406a6e","tid":2023763,"uid":246648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFbsZhG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFbsZhG.jpg&h=5be3f9dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3578d0afd69781dcb4b69b18ccbb61018be379a3","tid":2023763,"uid":231600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4e766541c1eb97ad7c47941354d6cac98406a6e","tid":2023763,"uid":246648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFbsZhG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFbsZhG.jpg&h=5be3f9dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:25:38.000Z","msg":"你是烏賊"},{"pid":"41281e06c9018f7085543356092ba9d751ce623a","tid":2023763,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:34:22.000Z","msg":"我推了"},{"pid":"548d9674ed0cab726d1432243bca6a070e2b9b8b","tid":2023763,"uid":231600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41281e06c9018f7085543356092ba9d751ce623a","tid":2023763,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:34:22.000Z","msg":"我推了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"謝謝你"},{"pid":"3e3df6d6d780408d13f09b411d0ba12e9b3b8980","tid":2023763,"uid":212999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:51:50.000Z","msg":"偶像本質就係曇花一現<br />\n佢體現出黎既野唔係偶像本人真實樣子<br />\n而係粉絲心內的理想偶像的樣子"},{"pid":"1f29816f7d56a357be72af2f13d747aed856e39d","tid":2023763,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:07:18.000Z","msg":"她們只是「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雞，妓女，她們什麼都不是！</span></span>」"},{"pid":"6ef82dabe241754afe424719881b2eeb337c0844","tid":2023763,"uid":134174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:31:13.000Z","msg":"山本寬係WUG個講法唔錯"},{"pid":"71e573e6c24c2534e296003caf39c26646d9c1cb","tid":2023763,"uid":112081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:38:34.000Z","msg":"去睇偶像大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}